title: Can you still get the Star Guardian icon from the quiz?

embed.description: They are protectors blazing bright, yet destined to collapse as furiously as they burn. They are the Star Guardians.

body: I want to know if it's still possible to get the Star Guardian icon. Was it just something in a limited time frame? I did the quiz and no messages are popping up about the icon.

replies.body: I don't remember the exact dates at the moment, but that quiz has since ended already. You were only able to do the quiz for the icons when it first came up.

> [{quoted}](name=Broporo,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=LjAPyhXy,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2017-08-13T04:06:13.538+0000)

Oh okay. That sucks. Oh well.
